<section id="about" class="py-14 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-primary text-secondary overflow-hidden relative">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_0%_0%,rgba(160,174,192,0.05)_0%,transparent_50%)]"></div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 relative z-10">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-10 sm:gap-16 lg:gap-24">
      <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 relative group">
        <div class="absolute -inset-6 bg-accent/20 blur-[80px] rounded-full opacity-20 group-hover:opacity-40 transition-opacity duration-1000"></div>
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl glass-card">
          <img 
            src="/assets/mr-friday.jpg" 
            alt="Mr. Friday Igbunu Kelvin - Lead Carpenter & Owner" 
            class="w-full aspect-[4/5] object-cover transition-transform duration-[2000ms] group-hover:scale-110"
          />
        </div>
        
        <div class="absolute bottom-4 right-4 p-5 glass-card rounded-xl shadow-2xl backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/10 w-auto max-w-[200px] xs:max-w-[240px] group-hover:translate-x-1 group-hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform duration-500 z-20">
           <div class="h-0.5 w-8 bg-accent mb-3"></div>
           <p class="text-accent text-[8px] tracking-[.4em] uppercase font-black mb-1">Master Artisan</p>
           <h4 class="text-lg xs:text-xl font-serif font-black leading-tight text-white text-glow">Friday Igbunu <span class="text-accent italic">Kelvin</span></h4>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 mt-6 sm:mt-12 lg:mt-0">
        <div class="max-w-xl">
          <h2 class="text-accent text-[10px] tracking-[.4em] sm:tracking-[.6em] uppercase mb-3 sm:mb-4 font-black">Legacy & Craft</h2>
          <h3 class="text-3xl sm:text-5xl md:text-7xl font-serif font-black mb-6 sm:mb-10 leading-[1.1] text-glow">Mastering the <span class="text-accent underline decoration-accent/20 underline-offset-4 sm:underline-offset-8">Divine</span> Craft</h3>
          
          <div class="space-y-5 sm:space-y-8 text-gray-400 leading-relaxed font-sans text-sm sm:text-lg">
            <p>
              At the absolute core of White Wolf Furniture sits <span class="text-white font-bold tracking-tight">Mr. Friday Igbunu Kelvin</span>, our visionary lead carpenter and owner. With over a decade of dedication to the art of timber and steel, Kelvin bridges the gap between raw industrial utility and breathtaking artisanal elegance.
            </p>
            <p class="italic border-l-2 border-accent/30 pl-5 sm:pl-8 text-base sm:text-xl text-white/80 font-serif py-2">
              "Every project is a profound conversation between the raw medium and the soul of the owner. We don't just build furniture; we create heirlooms."
            </p>
            
            <div class="pt-6 sm:pt-10 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 sm:gap-10">
              <div class="glass-card p-5 sm:p-8 rounded-xl border border-white/10 hover:border-accent/40 active:border-accent/40 transition-colors">
                <p class="text-accent text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-serif font-black">15+</p>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-[9px] sm:text-[10px] tracking-[.3em] sm:tracking-[.4em] uppercase mt-2 sm:mt-3 font-bold">Years of Mastery</p>
              </div>
              <div class="glass-card p-5 sm:p-8 rounded-xl border border-white/10 hover:border-accent/40 active:border-accent/40 transition-colors">
                <p class="text-accent text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-serif font-black">500+</p>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-[9px] sm:text-[10px] tracking-[.3em] sm:tracking-[.4em] uppercase mt-2 sm:mt-3 font-bold">Projects Delivered</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
